maze.logic.Entity

    • Uses of Entity in maze.logic

      Subclasses of Entity in maze.logic 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Dragon
      The Dragon entity represents a static or dynamic object of the Maze that cannot be traversed (unless it's killed).
      class  Exit
      The Exit entity represents a static object of the Maze that can only be traversed when the Dragon(s) is/are killed.
      class  Hero
      The Hero entity represents a dynamic object of the Maze that cannot be traversed.
      class  Sword
      The Sword entity represents a static object of the Maze that can be traversed.
      class  Wall
      The Wall entity represents a static object of the Maze that cannot be traversed.
